                                                    <i class="fas fa-code" style="color: yellow;"></i> Asp.Net Core
                                                </span>
                                            </a>

                                            <a class="dropdown-item" href="/Blog/BlogByCategory/5/">
                                                <span style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; font-size: 16px;">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-code" style="color: green;"></i> Asp.Net Core WebApi
